  "texts": [
    "Evaluating various open and closed-source LLMs revealed significant limitations in handling questions involving rapidly changing knowledge and erroneous premises.",
    "Based on these findings, the study proposed a simple in-context learning method, FreshPrompt, significantly improving LLMs' performance on FreshQA by integrating relevant and up-to-date information sourced from search engines into the prompt.",
    "(5) Safety, Ethic, and Trustworthiness.",
    "To comprehensively evaluate the safety of LLMs, SafetyBench [358] implements an efficient and accurate evaluation of LLMs' safety through 11,435 multiple-choice questions covering 7 safety categories in multiple languages (Chinese and English).",
    "The diversity of question types and the broad data sources ensure rigorous testing of LLMs in various safety-related scenarios."
